1
00:01:49,359 --> 00:01:50,200
Five Stars suppress the evil

2
00:01:50,280 --> 00:01:51,079
Light illuminates the darkness

3
00:01:51,439 --> 00:01:53,400
Thousands of gods protect my spirit

4
00:01:53,719 --> 00:01:54,280
Dispel!

5
00:02:00,959 --> 00:02:02,000
What's wrong with Xiaobai?

6
00:02:02,879 --> 00:02:05,239
She went to Master Liu's room and got possessed.

7
00:02:05,480 --> 00:02:06,680
Possessed. Possessed.

8
00:02:15,159 --> 00:02:16,560
Then what is he doing?

9
00:02:19,719 --> 00:02:22,159
My master knows exorcism.

10
00:02:23,599 --> 00:02:25,240
Exorcism.

11
00:02:25,680 --> 00:02:28,199
How can you take this ghost talk seriously?

12
00:02:46,400 --> 00:02:47,479
Heed my command immediately.

13
00:02:56,840 --> 00:02:57,439
Speak.

14
00:02:57,879 --> 00:02:59,120
Why do you steal souls?

15
00:02:59,360 --> 00:03:00,159
And harm Master Liu?

16
00:03:01,960 --> 00:03:04,520
He had me sold here like an animal.

17
00:03:04,520 --> 00:03:07,240
And lost my life. He deserves to die.

18
00:03:15,319 --> 00:03:16,280
Where are you going?

19
00:03:16,719 --> 00:03:18,319
Could he be involved in Master Liu's death?

20
00:03:22,560 --> 00:03:24,120
I found you.

21
00:03:24,120 --> 00:03:25,400
I don't know you.

22
00:03:25,800 --> 00:03:26,639
I won't go.

23
00:03:33,400 --> 00:03:34,120
I'm sorry.

24
00:03:43,680 --> 00:03:45,560
You are Yu'er.

25
00:03:51,120 --> 00:03:52,400
It has nothing to do with me!

26
00:03:52,639 --> 00:03:53,479
It's not my fault.

27
00:03:53,840 --> 00:03:56,080
Blame the Manor Lord! Blame Master Liu!

28
00:03:56,520 --> 00:03:57,560
It's not my fault.

29
00:03:58,000 --> 00:03:58,840
Why blame them?

30
00:03:58,840 --> 00:03:59,879
It's not my fault.

31
00:04:01,120 --> 00:04:01,639
Speak.

32
00:04:04,919 --> 00:04:05,520
I'll speak.

33
00:04:05,840 --> 00:04:06,439
I'll speak.

34
00:04:07,199 --> 00:04:07,639
Back then...

35
00:04:08,520 --> 00:04:10,039
Master Liu's only son committed a crime.

36
00:04:11,199 --> 00:04:12,199
And was sentenced to beheading.

37
00:04:16,160 --> 00:04:16,800
Move it! Move it!

38
00:04:17,879 --> 00:04:19,480
He didn't want his son to die.

39
00:04:20,199 --> 00:04:21,720
So the Manor Lord had me find a...

40
00:04:22,079 --> 00:04:23,439
...child of fourteen or fifteen...

41
00:04:23,959 --> 00:04:25,839
...to replace Master Liu's son in prison.

42
00:04:27,279 --> 00:04:28,639
I specifically grabbed one...

43
00:04:28,639 --> 00:04:31,480
...with a build similar to Master Liu's son.

44
00:04:31,639 --> 00:04:32,560
Come save me! Take him away!

45
00:04:32,639 --> 00:04:32,959
Sister!

46
00:04:32,959 --> 00:04:33,879
I really thought...

47
00:04:34,040 --> 00:04:36,439
...he was just a begging orphan from West Street.

48
00:04:37,319 --> 00:04:39,399
I didn't know he had a sister.

49
00:04:40,199 --> 00:04:42,600
She went all over the capital to file complaints.

50
00:04:42,879 --> 00:04:44,240
She even beat the Dengwen Drum.

51
00:04:45,279 --> 00:04:46,040
It was Huang Cui.

52
00:04:46,360 --> 00:04:46,920
If you want to blame someone...

53
00:04:47,519 --> 00:04:48,399
...blame Master Liu.

54
00:04:49,120 --> 00:04:50,319
Blame the Manor Lord.

55
00:04:51,319 --> 00:04:52,480
You deserve to die too.

56
00:04:52,480 --> 00:04:55,160
Die! Everyone must die!

57
00:04:56,560 --> 00:04:57,199
I was wrong.

58
00:04:57,920 --> 00:04:58,839
I was wrong.

59
00:05:02,319 --> 00:05:03,879
Divine Physician, save me!

60
00:05:04,040 --> 00:05:05,120
I don't want to die!

61
00:05:05,360 --> 00:05:06,800
Save me! Save me!

62
00:05:07,680 --> 00:05:09,279
I'd rather be taken by the Yamen.

63
00:05:09,519 --> 00:05:12,120
I don't want to be taken by a vengeful spirit!

64
00:05:13,120 --> 00:05:13,800
Save me.

65
00:05:15,759 --> 00:05:16,439
I have money.

66
00:05:17,040 --> 00:05:17,879
I'll give it all to you.

67
00:05:18,240 --> 00:05:19,079
Save me.

68
00:05:19,839 --> 00:05:20,439
Save me.

69
00:05:20,439 --> 00:05:21,560
I'll give it all to you.

70
00:05:21,560 --> 00:05:22,079
Ding Xiong.

71
00:05:22,839 --> 00:05:24,920
I will send Yu'er's vengeful spirit away.

72
00:05:25,680 --> 00:05:26,639
You go back to your room and rest first.

73
00:05:27,639 --> 00:05:28,360
Okay, okay, okay.

74
00:05:29,040 --> 00:05:29,839
Thank you, thank you.

75
00:05:30,040 --> 00:05:30,639
Thank you.

76
00:05:32,360 --> 00:05:34,000
I'm sorry, I'm sorry.

77
00:05:42,360 --> 00:05:43,560
Take him back to his room.

78
00:05:43,800 --> 00:05:45,600
It wasn't me! It wasn't me!

79
00:05:55,000 --> 00:05:56,199
You worked hard today.

80
00:05:58,519 --> 00:06:00,680
I didn't expect Yu'er's fate to be so tragic.

81
00:06:01,759 --> 00:06:03,920
His sister Huang Cui also had a bitter life.

82
00:06:07,839 --> 00:06:08,480
Rest assured.

83
00:06:09,199 --> 00:06:10,720
I will definitely find out the truth.

84
00:06:11,399 --> 00:06:12,800
To comfort the spirits of the dead in heaven.

85
00:06:14,480 --> 00:06:15,000
Okay.

86
00:06:21,160 --> 00:06:22,759
How did you convince Xiaobai to help?

87
00:06:31,519 --> 00:06:32,560
Why are you here?

88
00:06:33,519 --> 00:06:34,480
The medicine and prescription...

89
00:06:34,480 --> 00:06:35,680
Didn't I send them to you?

90
00:06:36,839 --> 00:06:38,720
I heard from the servants you were brewing medicine.

91
00:06:38,879 --> 00:06:39,800
So I came to see you.

92
00:06:41,399 --> 00:06:43,199
How is your injury?

93
00:06:46,680 --> 00:06:47,480
Much better.

94
00:06:48,879 --> 00:06:50,000
About today...

95
00:06:50,399 --> 00:06:51,519
I have to thank you.

96
00:06:51,519 --> 00:06:53,120
You were injured saving me.

97
00:06:53,480 --> 00:06:54,560
I should be the one thanking you.

98
00:06:55,439 --> 00:06:57,639
So I asked Siniang to borrow the kitchen.

99
00:06:58,519 --> 00:07:00,240
And made a bowl of walnut paste just for you.

100
00:07:05,399 --> 00:07:05,959
Taste it.

101
00:07:12,800 --> 00:07:14,040
This is the first time I've eaten...

102
00:07:14,040 --> 00:07:15,199
...such large walnut chunks.

103
00:07:17,800 --> 00:07:19,759
But the Divine Physician's sweetheart loves it this way.

104
00:07:22,680 --> 00:07:25,199
It's my first time making it too.

105
00:07:28,079 --> 00:07:30,079
You have a favor to ask.

106
00:07:31,439 --> 00:07:33,319
Miss Xiaobai is indeed clever.

107
00:07:34,600 --> 00:07:37,800
There is indeed a matter I've been thinking about...

108
00:07:38,199 --> 00:07:39,759
...that only Miss Xiaobai can help me with.

109
00:07:44,879 --> 00:07:45,839
Let's hear it.

110
00:07:56,680 --> 00:07:57,319
All right.

111
00:07:57,879 --> 00:07:58,720
So straightforward.

112
00:07:59,800 --> 00:08:02,240
After all, I am indebted to you.

113
00:08:07,680 --> 00:08:08,639
Do you know about Huang Cui?

114
00:08:09,560 --> 00:08:10,639
I wonder if Lord Hua

115
00:08:11,199 --> 00:08:12,439
has the time

116
00:08:13,480 --> 00:08:14,480
to hear a story of mine.

117
00:08:21,279 --> 00:08:22,199
Two years ago,

118
00:08:22,560 --> 00:08:24,480
a woman named Huang Cui lost her younger brother.

119
00:08:25,720 --> 00:08:27,000
She searched the entire capital.

120
00:08:27,399 --> 00:08:28,560
She caused quite a stir.

121
00:08:30,439 --> 00:08:32,000
She even came to the Dali Temple back then.

122
00:08:32,759 --> 00:08:33,840
But without proof or evidence,

123
00:08:34,600 --> 00:08:35,320
no case could be established.

124
00:08:37,759 --> 00:08:39,879
Finally, Huang Cui was driven to desperation.

125
00:08:40,519 --> 00:08:43,039
She threatened suicide at the Jingzhao Yin office gate.

126
00:08:44,159 --> 00:08:45,879
Lord Meng didn't want to see her take her own life,

127
00:08:46,519 --> 00:08:48,600
so he promised to investigate the case thoroughly.

128
00:08:51,159 --> 00:08:52,320
The complaint for this case

129
00:08:52,960 --> 00:08:53,960
was written by me.

130
00:08:55,879 --> 00:08:57,120
Later, the office discovered

131
00:08:57,919 --> 00:08:58,919
that Huang Cui's brother

132
00:08:59,799 --> 00:09:01,200
had been sent to Baixiao Manor.

133
00:09:03,960 --> 00:09:04,679
What?

134
00:09:07,840 --> 00:09:09,039
Officials couldn't enter the Manor.

135
00:09:09,840 --> 00:09:11,440
Inquiries sent through others went unanswered.

136
00:09:16,120 --> 00:09:16,919
For these past two years,

137
00:09:17,320 --> 00:09:20,120
Lord Meng kept sending summons to the Manor.

138
00:09:21,039 --> 00:09:23,240
Finally, it was set for the eighth of last month

139
00:09:23,960 --> 00:09:24,960
to hold a hearing.

140
00:09:25,159 --> 00:09:25,840
The eighth.

141
00:09:28,279 --> 00:09:29,159
Half a month later,

142
00:09:29,159 --> 00:09:30,159
Lord Meng was murdered.

143
00:09:30,360 --> 00:09:31,200
On the eighth,

144
00:09:31,559 --> 00:09:32,639
we waited until the lamps were lit,

145
00:09:32,759 --> 00:09:33,799
but the Manor Lord never showed up.

146
00:09:34,519 --> 00:09:36,639
On the tenth, the Manor sent someone to report

147
00:09:36,879 --> 00:09:37,919
that the Manor Lord was missing.

148
00:09:38,200 --> 00:09:40,519
Lord Meng felt there was something fishy,

149
00:09:41,159 --> 00:09:42,559
so he decided to investigate both cases together.

150
00:09:43,559 --> 00:09:44,559
On the day of the incident,

151
00:09:45,000 --> 00:09:47,080
I was going to ask about the progress of Huang Cui's case.

152
00:09:47,960 --> 00:09:49,240
But when I arrived,

153
00:09:49,799 --> 00:09:51,639
Lord Meng never appeared.

154
00:10:28,120 --> 00:10:28,720
Take him away.

155
00:10:28,879 --> 00:10:29,559
Yes, sir.

156
00:10:33,720 --> 00:10:34,360
So,

157
00:10:35,639 --> 00:10:37,000
you sought out the Dali Temple

158
00:10:37,759 --> 00:10:40,519
and waded into the muddy waters of Baixiao Manor

159
00:10:41,440 --> 00:10:42,759
just to clear your own name.

160
00:10:43,039 --> 00:10:44,639
This isn't just my own wrongful case.

161
00:10:45,279 --> 00:10:46,679
If I didn't enter the fray,

162
00:10:47,279 --> 00:10:48,840
I fear there would be more injustices.

163
00:10:50,039 --> 00:10:51,200
In that case,

164
00:10:51,879 --> 00:10:53,080
it is the Crown Prince who wants to protect you.

165
00:10:54,679 --> 00:10:56,600
Then behind Baixiao Manor...

166
00:10:57,720 --> 00:10:58,759
is the Eunuch faction.

167
00:10:59,960 --> 00:11:00,600
Then the Crown Prince

168
00:11:00,679 --> 00:11:02,600
intends to use me against the Eunuch faction and the Empress Dowager.

169
00:11:03,200 --> 00:11:04,720
Then is the Emperor's health...

170
00:11:05,960 --> 00:11:07,279
If you speak any louder,

171
00:11:08,039 --> 00:11:09,679
you won't be needing that head of yours.

172
00:11:14,080 --> 00:11:15,639
Go get the ledger back first.

173
00:11:16,240 --> 00:11:17,240
After the commotion today,

174
00:11:17,960 --> 00:11:19,120
I'm afraid some people

175
00:11:19,919 --> 00:11:21,120
will try to destroy the evidence.

176
00:11:21,480 --> 00:11:22,360
That's exactly what I was thinking.

177
00:11:28,440 --> 00:11:30,399
Unlock the shackles. Focus on the case.

178
00:11:31,159 --> 00:11:32,639
According to what Ding Da just confessed,

179
00:11:33,320 --> 00:11:34,440
Yu'er must be the brother

180
00:11:34,440 --> 00:11:35,559
that Huang Cui has been looking for.

181
00:11:35,759 --> 00:11:36,519
Therefore,

182
00:11:37,120 --> 00:11:38,559
if we can find Huang Cui,

183
00:11:38,960 --> 00:11:41,879
perhaps we can catch Master Liu's killer.

184
00:11:51,559 --> 00:11:52,639
We searched all night,

185
00:11:53,279 --> 00:11:55,720
but found no trace of Yu'er or Huang Cui.

186
00:11:57,200 --> 00:11:58,799
I've already sent a message to the Dali Temple,

187
00:11:59,039 --> 00:11:59,879
asking them to look for

188
00:12:00,519 --> 00:12:01,960
Huang Cui's original complaint.

189
00:12:11,159 --> 00:12:13,399
If I were Huang Cui,

190
00:12:16,120 --> 00:12:18,279
knowing my brother's death

191
00:12:18,919 --> 00:12:20,679
was related to the Manor,

192
00:12:21,240 --> 00:12:22,879
I would certainly try every means

193
00:12:22,879 --> 00:12:24,879
to sneak into the Manor and avenge him.

194
00:12:27,600 --> 00:12:28,679
Ding Da said

195
00:12:29,080 --> 00:12:31,600
Yu'er was fourteen or fifteen back then.

196
00:12:33,399 --> 00:12:34,919
Then his sister, Huang Cui...

197
00:12:35,399 --> 00:12:35,960
how old is she?

198
00:12:36,279 --> 00:12:39,080
The complaint lists her birth as the winter of the 8th year of Qingde.

199
00:12:39,799 --> 00:12:40,639
Around twenty.

200
00:12:41,759 --> 00:12:43,879
Around twenty.

201
00:12:44,440 --> 00:12:45,480
Like an orphan.

202
00:12:47,000 --> 00:12:48,960
Meaning she has no home in the capital.

203
00:12:50,679 --> 00:12:52,360
And she's a woman.

204
00:12:55,279 --> 00:12:55,879
I know who it is.

205
00:12:56,279 --> 00:12:56,919
Know what?

206
00:12:57,320 --> 00:12:57,919
It's her.

207
00:13:02,159 --> 00:13:03,519
Where are you going so early?
